      "writtenOn": "2020-04-30T15:31:26Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Yeah, now that said, many of us are eager to use parts of Abseil that are viable, like btree_map, the hash framework, or all that absl/debugging stuff for testing code.  I don\u0027t think this is a complete wash, just that certain parts of Abseil must stay carved out.",
